Bear Marketing, located in the dynamic West End of Brisbane, seeks a highly
skilled Web Developer with a strong design sensibility. We specialise in
delivering high-quality, impactful web solutions that drive tangible results
for our diverse clientele. If you have a passion for crafting engaging, high-
converting websites and are ready to contribute to our clients' success, we
invite you to apply.

** Why Join Bear Marketing? **

  * Collaborate with a dedicated and high-achieving team. 
  * Engage in a wide range of web development projects for various clients. 
  * Enjoy the creative and professional environment of our West End office. 
  * Make a significant contribution to our clients' growth and success. 
  * Your exceptional work will be recognised and valued.   

** Responsibilities: **

  * Design and execute comprehensive web development projects, from the design stage through to full WordPress implementation, including landing pages and essential web assets. 
  * Develop and integrate a wide range of web functionalities, such as eCommerce platforms, product feeds, customer relationship management (CRM) systems, and other third-party services, ensuring seamless operation and user experience. 
  * Implement effective search engine optimisation (SEO) strategies to enhance online visibility and drive targeted traffic to our clients' websites. 
  * Take charge of web projects from initiation to completion, adhering to defined scopes, timelines, and quality standards, while proactively communicating progress and challenges. 
  * Apply best practices in conversion rate optimisation to ensure web projects achieve tangible outcomes, analysing performance data to inform ongoing optimisation efforts. 
  * Lead the technical aspects of web project delivery, including site architecture decisions, coding standards, and performance optimisation, to ensure high-quality user experiences. 
  * Demonstrate effective project management skills, efficiently organising and prioritising multiple projects and components to meet deadlines and client expectations.   

** Requirements ** : 

  * At least 2 years of experience in Web Design, supported by a portfolio of your work. 
  * Proficiency in WordPress, with solid skills in Figma, Adobe XD, and Sketch for design and prototyping. 
  * Exceptional design capability, with a knack for creating visually appealing web pages that align with brand identity. 
  * Competence in HTML and CSS for website customisation, with PHP and JavaScript knowledge being an advantage. 
  * Strong organisational skills to handle multiple projects and components to completion. 
  * Excellent communication skills, capable of effective independent and team collaboration. 

** Apply Now **

Bear Marketing values a strong work ethic, creativity, and the ability to
deliver outstanding web solutions. If you're driven to excel in web design and
development and can see yourself contributing to our vision, please apply with
examples of your work. We look forward to welcoming you to our team and
working together to achieve great results.

